pe="seg" mid="6">Economische voordelen</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="6"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">1/DfHrhvCjBK/LwBw92hoiO1rpY=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="796ad5f1-fc09-48e0-835e-2082b822cd42"><source>The battery is charged during low electricity price periods and discharges energy to the grid during high electricity price periods, maximizing returns.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="7">The battery is charged during low electricity price periods and discharges energy to the grid during high electricity price periods, maximizing returns.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="7">The battery is charged during low electricity price periods and discharges energy to the grid during high electricity price periods, maximizing returns.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="7" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">CcWpgx42ldPOKfIYgkQ9PC2excY=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group></body></file></xliff>